162
0:23:17.000 --> 0:23:25.000
has there been work to coordinate with the definition of Open Standards and the Open Knowledge Centre's work on defining Open Standards?

163
0:23:25.000 --> 0:23:38.000
So when the European Commission is writing their initial proposal for legislation, a lot of it is behind the actual drafting, it happens internally in the Commission.

